Polpx to Start Second Daily Power Auction for Next-Day Delivery

-- B y   M a r e k   S t r z e l e c k i
-- 
2011-02-11T16:12:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/polpx-to-start-second-daily-power-auction-for-next-day-delivery.html
Polpx , the Warsaw-based electricity
exchange, will introduce a second daily auction for next-day
power, the bourse said.  The new auction will be at 10:30 a.m. local time as of Feb.
22, the company said today on its  website . The first sale for
next-day power is at 8 a.m.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marek Strzelecki in Warsaw 
 mstrzelecki1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Voss at   sev@bloomberg.net  